<h3 class="date"><a href="/2006/dec/08/">&#x27a0;</a> December 8, 2006</h3>


<div class="row">
    <div class="span12">


    
    <div class="well" id="the_dvd_wars" >

        
        <a name="003163"></a>
        

        <h4><a class="taggedlink linklink" href="http://www.thedvdwars.com/">The DVD Wars</a></h4>

        

        <p>Tracking the popularity of the competing blue-laser DVD formats by comparing Amazon data.  Very smart.  HD-DVD is winning at the moment.  (Wonder if that&#8217;s just because people getting HD TVs are searching for &#8220;DVD HD&#8221;?)  Let&#8217;s see how the PS3 affects this.</p>

        <div class="row-fluid">
            <div class="span10">
                
