        <a name="002934"></a>
        

        <h4><a class="taggedlink linklink" href="http://amazon.com/o/ASIN/1844137864/groovymother-20/ref=nosim/">Amazon.com: Wall and Piece: Books: BANKSY</a></h4>

        

        <p>If you&#8217;re just hearing about Bansky this weekend, might I recommend this book.  It&#8217;s a compendium of his finest work, and it&#8217;s truly impressive &#8212; both funny and thought-provoking.  But mostly funny.</p>

