<h3 class="date"><a href="/2006/feb/07/">&#x27a0;</a> February 7, 2006</h3>


<div class="row">
    <div class="span12">


    
    <div class="well" id="refund_please" >

        
        <a name="002255"></a>
        

        <h4><a class="taggedlink linklink" href="http://refundplease.com/">Refund Please</a></h4>

        

        <p>Keep track of items you purchase from Amazon &#8212; If they drop the price within 30 days, you can get a quibble-free refund.  I got back $9 from them today for four CDs I purchased last month!  I might try and make a bookmarklet or GreaseMonkey script to handle this automagically.</p>

        <div class="row-fluid">
            <div class="span10">
                
                    Filed under
                    
                        : <a rel="tag" class="tag" href="/tag/amazon/">amazon</a>
                    
                
            </div>
            <div class="span2" style="text-align: right;">
                
                    <a rel="via" href="http://www.consumerist.com/consumer/shophacks/amazon-credits-you-becomes-refundpleasecom-152533.php" title="I found this link at...">via</a> |
                
                
                    
                
